item.description:
@Zenzie wrote:

Main fact , Too many peeps use hamachi when I used to click on it it had the same like you have but it gave a warning :" Too many connections , you want to keep reconnecting?"

Just wait.

If it isn’t this problem go to program files typ in “H” from Hamachi till you see the map and try to double click on the HAM icon in that map . Mine does work only in the map
